cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE. 

The paper deals with machine reading at scale, which involves both information retrieval and reading comprehension tasks. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Among these categories, cs.CL and cs.IR are the most likely as they directly relate to the tasks performed in the paper.
